race.comment: SCOTT CHARISMA (6) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 2.75 lengths into third (22.45) at this track in a Mix 6/7 over 390m. Key chance in this line up. JODIE'S ANGEL (7) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (22.35) at Ballarat. Key player if finds best. ABOVE THEM ALL (1) got around 400m in a swift 22.62 when winning a Restricted WIN at Geelong last start. Harder here but expected to feature again. RED TURTLE (8) placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.
